        x = -8.773321
        x = -8.773321
        x = -8.773321
        x = -8.773321
        x = -8.773321
        [1] 0 0 0 5

Setting the seed value and it starts working.

        > set.seed(1)
        > rwRcpp(2,5)
        x = -0.626454
        x = 0.183643
        x = -0.835629
        x = 1.595281
        x = 0.329508
        x = -0.820468
        x = 0.487429
        x = 0.738325
        x = 0.575781
        [1] 3 0 1 1

Opening a now R session, I tested also the following.

        > source("rw.r")
        > rwRcpp(2,5)
        x = -8.773321
